channel.title: 2 Annoying Things!
channel.description:
I just compiled after i tryed to rip prestige from rune world and i got these 2 errors
[code=java]source\server\model\players\DialogueHandler.java:54: error: cannot find symbol c.isMaxed(); ^ symbol: method isMaxed() location: variable c of type Client source\server\model\players\DialogueHandler.java:65: error: cannot find symbol c.getPA().resetLevels(); ^ symbol: method resetLevels() location: class PlayerAssistant Note: Some input files use unchecked or unsafe operations. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:unchecked for details. 2 errors Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
If someone could please help I would really appreciate it. I will get my friend to rep+ you thanks.
